management.

Implement partial match for booking descriptions

To enhance user experience and search flexibility, the search algorithm
has been added to support partial matches. This change allows users to
find bookings with descriptions that contains the search keywords.

This update is expected to significantly improve the usability of the
search feature, making it more intuitive and forgiving, especially in
cases where exact descriptions are difficult to recall.
